# Jeevan Setu v2 — National-Scale Emergency Command Platform

Transform the existing academic-grade emergency coordination app into a visually stunning, production-ready, government-grade Smart City 112 Command Center.

## Proposed Changes

### Backend Architecture Evolution

Refactor the monolithic `backend/` into a modular service-layer architecture within the same FastAPI app (keeping monorepo, single deploy). All existing routes and models are preserved and enhanced.

---

#### [NEW] [config.py](file:///home/anand/Documents/jeevan-setu/backend/config.py)
- Centralized settings using `pydantic-settings` (replaces scattered `os.getenv` calls)

#### [models.py](file:///home/anand/Documents/jeevan-setu/backend/models.py)
- Add `admin` role to `UserRole` enum
- Add new models: `IncidentTimeline`, `AuditLog`, `ChatMessage`, `Notification`, `RefreshToken`
- Add indexes and soft-delete support

#### [schemas.py](file:///home/anand/Documents/jeevan-setu/backend/schemas.py)
- Add schemas for new models (chat, analytics, admin, notifications)
- Add WebSocket event schemas

#### [dispatch.py](file:///home/anand/Documents/jeevan-setu/backend/dispatch.py)
- Replace simple Haversine-only logic with weighted scoring: `distance(0.5) + severity_match(0.25) + workload(0.15) + capability(0.1)`
- Add surge mode detection and hospital load balancing

#### [NEW] [events.py](file:///home/anand/Documents/jeevan-setu/backend/events.py)
- Event bus abstraction with typed event schemas (IncidentCreated, AmbulanceAssigned, etc.)
- In-process pub/sub (ready for Redis upgrade)

#### [NEW] [middleware.py](file:///home/anand/Documents/jeevan-setu/backend/middleware.py)
- Rate limiting middleware, audit logging, structured JSON logging, secure headers

#### [NEW] [routes/admin_routes.py](file:///home/anand/Documents/jeevan-setu/backend/routes/admin_routes.py)
- System stats, all incidents, all ambulances/hospitals, user management

#### [NEW] [routes/analytics_routes.py](file:///home/anand/Documents/jeevan-setu/backend/routes/analytics_routes.py)
- Incident trends, response time stats, ambulance utilization, hospital occupancy

#### [NEW] [routes/chat_routes.py](file:///home/anand/Documents/jeevan-setu/backend/routes/chat_routes.py)
- Chat message CRUD, incident-based chat sessions

#### [main.py](file:///home/anand/Documents/jeevan-setu/backend/main.py)
- Add new routers, middleware, structured logging setup
- Enhanced WebSocket handler with chat message support

#### [auth.py](file:///home/anand/Documents/jeevan-setu/backend/auth.py)
- Add refresh token rotation support

#### [seed.py](file:///home/anand/Documents/jeevan-setu/backend/seed.py)
- Add admin user, more ambulances/hospitals across multiple cities, sample incidents for demo

